{"TopicId":162886,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"[1.3] [WIP] Suit Refuel","CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T17:38:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T17:38:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello. Please look at my first \u003Cstrong\u003Epart\u003C/strong\u003E-addon. Work in progress.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis part is for refueling your jetpack in EVA.\u00A0\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003EThe propellant is taken from the ship\u0027s supplies.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022MKKz.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.yapx.ru/MKKz.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload beta version:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/HuXTUS/KSP-SuitRefuelPlugin/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/HuXTUS/KSP-SuitRefuelPlugin/releases\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLicense: MIT\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/HuXTUS/KSP-SuitRefuelPlugin/blob/master/LICENSE\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/HuXTUS/KSP-SuitRefuelPlugin/blob/master/LICENSE\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m really bad at drawing, and Blender and Unity I downloaded a week ago. If someone wants to participate and make a model of this \u0022closet\u0022 for me, I will be happy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thiagobs","CreatedById":76021,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T19:31:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s quite neat! Especially the animation, looks like something out of an 60\u0027s/70\u0027s scifi show \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T22:02:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223110985\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162886\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499189897\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022178977\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HuXTUS\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, HuXTUS said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello. Please look at my first \u003Cstrong\u003Epart\u003C/strong\u003E-addon. Work in progress.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis part is for refueling your jetpack in EVA.\u00A0\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003EThe propellant is taken from the ship\u0027s supplies.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m really bad at drawing, and Blender and Unity I downloaded a week ago. If someone wants to participate and make a model of this \u0022closet\u0022 for me, I will be happy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is particularly awesome! \u00A0I look forward to now using it for my Jeremiah Maneuvers when it is necessary for me to get out and push.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould it be possible please to add in the transfer of resources for Life Support and Electricity as well?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T22:26:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTake a look at EVAFuel. \u00A0Let me know when it is complete, I will make sure they are compatible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-05T11:27:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks guys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F162886-13-wip-suit-refuel%252F\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022color:inherit;\u0022 title=\u0022Go to theJesuit\u0027s profile\u0022\u003EtheJesuit\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#272a34;\u0022\u003EWould it be possible please to add in the transfer of resources for Life Support and Electricity as well?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have not tried to play with mods (not so long ago I met the game), including Life Support. But I consulted with those who play with Life Support.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHis comment (my translation):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe LS-resources of the spacesuit is enough for 2 hours. 2 hours to work in EVA is a lot. You\u0027re not going to throw your kerbal out of the ship for a longer time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe propellant ends much faster.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you agree? We can discuss.\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#272a34;\u0022\u003EPeace. )\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#272a34;\u0022\u003EPS:\u00A0Maybe I can add a strings of resource names\u00A0to the cfg-file, which will be transmitted with propellant.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F162886-13-wip-suit-refuel%252F\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022color:inherit;\u0022 title=\u0022Go to linuxgurugamer\u0027s profile\u0022\u003Elinuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI saw \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/AliceTheGorgon/EvaFuel/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EEVAFuel \u003C/a\u003Ebefore. I\u0027m almost sure that the mods will be compatible. I\u0027m doing the usual Part that does something, I do not touch the logic that refers to the EVAFuel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-05T11:29:48Z\u0022 title=\u002207/05/2017 11:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 5, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by HuXTUS\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T09:01:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust joke\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022MTq4.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.yapx.ru/MTq4.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-06T18:33:46Z\u0022 title=\u002207/06/2017 06:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 6, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by HuXTUS\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T09:48:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022122369\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@theJesuit\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0hi,\u00A0\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003Ewhat do you think?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn right click menu of \u003Cstrong\u003Epart\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Eadded settings, y\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003Eou can select behavior for resources inside of EVA-suit (In, Out, Do nothing)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022W-qwHukXMp8.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/5873/W-qwHukXMp8.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nResult for settings on screenshot above:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022MaQZ.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.yapx.ru/MaQZ.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-08T10:08:44Z\u0022 title=\u002207/08/2017 10:08  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 8, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by HuXTUS\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T10:30:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223114684\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162886\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499507284\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022178977\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HuXTUS\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, HuXTUS said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022122369\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@theJesuit\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0hi,\u00A0\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003Ewhat do you think?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn right click menu of \u003Cstrong\u003Epart\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Eadded settings, y\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003Eou can select behavior for resources inside of EVA-suit (In, Out, Do nothing)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/5873/W-qwHukXMp8.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022W-qwHukXMp8.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/5873/W-qwHukXMp8.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E